[normal]Any factual information you have to offer from which [bold]the committee might be able to draw conclusions, or which could be put to other witnesses for their reactions.[bold]The conclusion I draw from this is that London has already some great working models to implement compliant routing that could include location a
[normal]nd time specific restrictions around the cycle network.  Our London Lorry Route Approver (
[normal]www.londonlorrycontrol.com
[normal]) could be configured to include these restrictions as could the TFL FJP.  
[normal]Please also note that a 
[normal]high risk 
[normal]of accident
[normal]s
